Objective:
Predict Airbnb listing price, room type, and/or occupancy using property images + tabular features.

Inputs (X):
•	Image of the property
•	Structured data: amenities, neighborhood, reviews, host info

Outputs (y):
•	Regression: Price (continuous)
•	Classification: Room type (entire, private, shared), availability category

DL Type:
•	Supervised learning
•	CNN + multimodal fusion

Business / Research Metrics:
•	Primary: MAE, RMSE (price), Accuracy (classification)
•	Secondary: R², F1-score (if classification is imbalanced)

Constraints:
•	Moderate dataset (~5k images) → transfer learning recommended
•	Variable image quality and size → preprocessing / resizing needed
•	explainability (Grad-CAM, SHAP)
